{
  "title": "Subglacial hydropotential of Antarctica",
  "description": "Antarctic subglacial gridded hydropotential (hydraulic potential) calculated using Shreve (1972) hydropotential equation using BedMachine Antarctica bed and ice topographies and firn air content (Morlighem et al., 2020; Morlighem, 2022). The dataset provides calculated hydropotential computed at 500 m resolution in EPSG:3031 (Polar Stereographic South) projection. The hydropotential is provided in kilopascals (kPa) and is distributed in both chunked NetCDF4 and cloud-optimized Zarr formats.",
